<p>Our diagnostic fee is $65, waived when you approve the repair. Gas valve replacement typically runs $180-280 depending on your LG model — that includes the OEM valve assembly and professional installation. We only use genuine LG parts, never aftermarket valves that fail quickly. Most homeowners find this reasonable when they realize the safety risks and specialized tools required for proper gas work.</p>
